{"tid":34111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解CC台班手足要咁專制？","createTime":"2016-12-11T09:35:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T12:41:02.000Z","uid":31314,"like":19,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ba3af0520cbbd3670302d6f6752a37f425a6ae2","tid":34111,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:35:07.000Z","msg":"每個台都有自己文化架啦<br />\n人不犯我，我不犯人<br />\n人地冇搞到你，你又何必拙拙迫人呢？<br />\n好似動物台咁，人地用咩睇片關你撚事咩？你憑咩去反對人地用大陸app睇片。仲話唔好睇中文字幕，要睇英文字幕。<br />\n你又唔去屌潮流台班人上淘寶？On9！<br />\n<br />\n波台又係，每個台都有自己文化，佢地鍾意打5p字咪由得佢地，佢地有冇係cc台打5p字？有冇搞到你地？咁你地又可必話入侵波台，收返波台等等？<br />\n<br />\n根本好多野都係你地一班憤青，睇唔過眼人地做既野而發生，人地講野唔啱聽，5毛，打5p字，5毛<br />\n總之乜柒都係錯既，cc台就最好最勁，咁你地玩撚埋佢啦！慢慢鍵國啦！"},{"pid":"b8a714c09b0c9395c47547d4678b669b962e6e6f","tid":34111,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:37:26.000Z","msg":"覺得波台要幫藍波狗爭取返個玩具台返泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcde894eccf515540c864bb530c7320ddf4c7a7b","tid":34111,"uid":3974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:38:29.000Z","msg":"吾短 <br />\n吾明<br />\n典刀巧拉 <br />\n十卜ching"},{"pid":"0bda7ae41ce83fdb560b98cb3d556c835b5ca0b5","tid":34111,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:40:05.000Z","msg":"活在自己世界<br />\n成日幻想自己喺到救世<br />\n所以優越感特別強"},{"pid":"e70bc9ee2bb26c7028f1829ca2f6e26f12005bac","tid":34111,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:40:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得波台要幫藍波狗爭取返個玩具台返泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n藍波撚有黑洞就夠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2cad47281bd247d87872056041948b5fe914645","